      "speaker": "AGENT",
      "text": "I'm sorry to hear about your vision. We have several experienced ophthalmologists available. Would you prefer to see Dr. Parul Maheshwari Sharma, Dr. Shuchi Verma, Dr. Purnima Sood, Dr. Deepa Gupta, or Dr. Digvijay Singh?"
