      "speaker": "AGENT",
      "text": "Thank you for that information, Lakshmi. The earliest available appointments are today, Thursday the sixteenth, at five o'clock in the evening with either Dr. Parul Maheshwari Sharma or Dr. Digvijay Singh. Would you like to book one of those?"
    },
