      "text": "Great choice. To confirm, that is Dr. Parul Maheshwari Sharma for a new consultation today, Thursday the sixteenth, at five o'clock in the evening. Could you please provide your 10-digit mobile number so I can finalize the booking for you?"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "PATIENT",
      "text": "Sure, it's 9811111000. Oh, wait, sorry, it ends in zero-zero-nine, that's 9811111009."
    },
    {
      "speaker": "AGENT",
      "text": "Your appointment is confirmed, Lakshmi. You are booked with Dr. Parul Maheshwari Sharma for a new consultation today, Thursday the sixteenth, at five o'clock in the evening. The consultation fee is 1600 INR. Is there anything else I can help you with today?"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "PATIENT",
      "text": "No, that's all, thank you so much for your help. Goodbye!"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "AGENT",
      "text": "You're very welcome, Lakshmi. We look forward to seeing you at five o'clock. Have a good day and goodbye!"
